      <h2 class="main--title">Check the top companies 🏆</h2>
      <p>First, it's important to understand how Gender Ratio, Race Ratio and the Diversity Score are calculated.</p>
<code># of male employees / # of female employees = Gender Ratio</code>
<code># of caucasian employees / # of black, asian, middle easter and latino employees = Race Ratio</code>
<code>Gender Ratio + Diversity Ratio = Score</code>

<p>Given that more equal numbers represent more diversity, the lower the score, the higher the company is in the rankings.</p>

